<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>9Slidevibe_tech</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
    <meta name="description" content="Explore amazing products at Your Store. Laptops, headphones, projectors, and more. Great deals and fast shipping!">
    <meta property="og:title" content="Your Store - Amazing Products at Great Prices">
    <meta property="og:description" content="Shop now for the best deals on tech gadgets, wireless headphones, laptops, and more.">
    <meta property="og:image" content="https://example.com/images/store-banner.jpg">
    <meta property="og:url" content="https://example.com">
</head>
<body>

<header>
    <h1>Welcome to 9Slidevibe_tech</h1>
    <nav>
        <ul class="nav-links">
            <li><a href="#home" onclick="showSection('home')">Home</a></li>
            <li><a href="#products" onclick="showSection('products')">Products</a></li>
            <li><a href="#shipping" onclick="showSection('shipping')">Shipping</a></li>
            <li><a href="#payment" onclick="showSection('payment')">Payment</a></li>
            <li><a href="#contact" onclick="showSection('contact')">Contact</a></li>
            <li><a href="#tracking" onclick="showSection('tracking')">Track Order</a></li>
        </ul>
    </nav>
    <button class="menu-button" aria-label="Toggle navigation menu" onclick="toggleMenu()">☰</button>
</header>

<main>
    <!-- Home Section -->
    <section id="home">
        <h2></h2>
        <div class="section-content">
            <p>Welcome to 9slidevibe_tec. Explore our amazing products!</p>
            <div class="slideshow-container">
                <!-- Slideshow images here -->
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="products" class="hidden">
        <h2>Products</h2>
        <div class="section-content product-list">
    
            <!-- Product 1: HP Pavilion Laptop -->
            <div class="product-card">
                <img src="https://www.bhphotovideo.com/images/images2500x2500/hp_5yh29ua_aba_pavilion_laptop_15_cs2010nr_core_1473122.jpg" alt="HP Pavilion Laptop" loading="lazy">
                <h3>HP Pavilion 15" Laptop</h3>
                <p>The HP Pavilion 15" laptop is designed for performance and portability. Equipped with an Intel Core i7 processor, 16GB RAM, and 512GB SSD, this lightweight powerhouse is ideal for multitasking and entertainment on the go.</p>
                <button>Add to Cart</button>
            </div>
    
            <!-- Product 2: Wireless Earbuds -->
            <div class="product-card">
                <img src="https://sc01.alicdn.com/kf/HTB1mX1UeBcHL1JjSZFBq6yiGXXa7/229999387/HTB1mX1UeBcHL1JjSZFBq6yiGXXa7.jpg" alt="Wireless Earbuds" loading="lazy">
                <h3>Wireless Bluetooth Earbuds</h3>
                <p>Experience true wireless freedom with these Bluetooth 5.0 earbuds. Featuring immersive sound quality, a compact charging case, and water-resistant design, they are perfect for workouts, commuting, or everyday use.</p>
                <button>Add to Cart</button>
            </div>
    
            <!-- Product 3: 4K Smart TV -->
            <div class="product-card">
                <img src="https://i5.walmartimages.com/asr/31d23744-3a9f-4bc6-88cd-bda390bab17e.9b9212a7dd5d6be8175ff3645610dce4.jpeg" alt="4K Smart TV" loading="lazy">
                <h3>50" 4K UHD Smart TV</h3>
                <p>Upgrade your viewing experience with this 50" 4K UHD Smart TV. It features a stunning ultra-HD resolution, vibrant colors, and built-in streaming apps like Netflix and Hulu for endless entertainment.</p>
                <button>Add to Cart</button>
            </div>
    
            <!-- Product 4: Beats Studio Wireless Headphones -->
            <div class="product-card">
                <img src="https://www.bhphotovideo.com/images/images2500x2500/beats_by_dr_dre_900_00109_01_studio_wireless_headphones_red_1016369.jpg" alt="Beats Studio Wireless Headphones" loading="lazy">
                <h3>Beats Studio Wireless Headphones</h3>
                <p>Get premium sound quality with the Beats Studio wireless headphones. Active noise cancellation, a comfortable over-ear design, and up to 22 hours of battery life make them perfect for music lovers on the go.</p>
                <button>Add to Cart</button>
            </div>
    
            <!-- Product 5: Samsung Freestyle Projector -->
            <div class="product-card">
                <img src="https://spy.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/Samsung-Freestyle-Review-15-of-15.jpg?resize=300" alt="Samsung Freestyle Projector" loading="lazy">
                <h3>Samsung Freestyle Projector</h3>
                <p>Transform any space into a cinema with the Samsung Freestyle portable projector. Compact yet powerful, it supports up to 100" screens and delivers sharp, vibrant visuals, making it perfect for movies, presentations, or gaming.</p>
                <button>Add to Cart</button>
            </div>
    
            <!-- Product 6: High-Tech Gadget Bundle -->
            <div class="product-card">
                <img src="https://3.bp.blogspot.com/-fVbBq-wXBag/WpjxatXevkI/AAAAAAAAAwg/sMLPiBhz9FMrDyJTTl-mB_z4zO59zHLHgCEwYBhgL/s1600/Tech-Gadget-1.jpg" alt="Tech Gadget Bundle" loading="lazy">
                <h3>Ultimate Tech Gadget Bundle</h3>
                <p>This bundle includes the latest tech gadgets, from portable power banks to smart home assistants. Stay connected and enjoy convenience with this must-have bundle for tech enthusiasts.</p>
                <button>Add to Cart</button>
            </div>
    
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Shipping Section -->
    <section id="shipping" class="hidden">
        <h2>Shipping Information</h2>
        <div class="section-content">
            <p>We offer worldwide shipping. Orders are typically processed within 2-3 business days, and shipping times vary depending on your location:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>USA: 3-5 business days</li>
                <li>Europe: 5-7 business days</li>
                <li>Rest of the World: 7-14 business days</li>
            </ul>
            <p>Free shipping on orders over $100.</p>
            <h3>Enter Your Shipping Details:</h3>
            <form id="shipping-form">
                <label for="full-name">Full Name:</label>
                <input type="text" id="full-name" name="full-name" placeholder="Your Name" required>

                <label for="address">Address:</label>
                <input type="text" id="address" name="address" placeholder="Your Shipping Address" required>

                <label for="city">City:</label>
                <input type="text" id="city" name="city" placeholder="Your City" required>

                <label for="postal-code">Postal Code:</label>
                <input type="text" id="postal-code" name="postal-code" placeholder="Your Postal Code" required>

                <label for="country">Country:</label>
                <input type="text" id="country" name="country" placeholder="Your Country" required>

                <button type="submit">Submit Shipping Details</button>
            </form>

            <div id="shipping-confirmation">
                <!-- Confirmation or errors will appear here -->
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Payment Section -->
    <section id="payment" class="hidden">
        <h2>Payment Information</h2>
        <div class="section-content">
            <p>We accept the following payment methods:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Credit/Debit Cards (Visa, MasterCard, AMEX)</li>
                <li>PayPal</li>
                <li>Bank Transfer</li>
            </ul>
            <h3>Your Cart</h3>
            <div id="cart">
                <p>No items in cart.</p>
            </div>
            <button onclick="proceedToPayment()">Proceed to Payment</button>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Contact Section -->
    <section id="contact" class="hidden">
        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <div class="section-content">
            <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, feel free to reach out to us:</p>
            <form id="contact-form">
                <label for="name">Your Name:</label>
                <input type="text" id="name" name="name" placeholder="Your Full Name" required>

                <label for="email">Your Email:</label>
                <input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="Your Email" required>

                <label for="message">Your Message:</label>
                <textarea id="message" name="message" placeholder="Write your message here..." required></textarea>

                <button type="submit">Send Message</button>
            </form>

            <div id="contact-response">
                <!-- Response from the store will appear here -->
            </div>

            <p>Alternatively, you can contact us at:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Email: support@yourstore.com</li>
                <li>Phone: +123 456 789</li>
                <li>Address: 123 Main Street, City, Country</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Track Order Section -->
    <section id="tracking" class="hidden">
        <h2>Track Your Order</h2>
        <div class="section-content">
            <p>Enter your order number to track the status of your shipment:</p>
            <form id="track-order-form">
                <label for="order-number">Order Number:</label>
                <input type="text" id="order-number" name="order-number" placeholder="Enter your order number">
                <button type="submit">Track Order</button>
            </form>
            <div id="tracking-results">
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</main>

<footer>
    <p>&copy; 2024 9Slidevibe_tech. All rights reserved.</p>
</footer>

<script src="script.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
